00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:21,240
Pardon me!

6
00:00:23,270 --> 00:00:25,020
Good evening!

7
00:00:25,020 --> 00:00:26,320
Koichi.

8
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,720
